<h2>General Software Review and Comparison Directories</h2>
<p>These are the biggest platforms where B2B buyers compare tools before purchasing. A listing here puts your product in front of high-intent buyers actively searching for software in your category.</p>
<p><strong>1. G2</strong> ,  2,000+ software categories. 5.5M+ buyers visit monthly. Grid reports rank products by user satisfaction. Free basic listing. DR 90+. The most influential <a href="/blog/analyze-competitor-keywords/">software review platform</a> for B2B buyers.</p>
<p><strong>2. Capterra</strong> ,  1.5M+ verified reviews across 800+ categories. Gartner-owned. Free basic listing. DR 85+. Capterra reviews appear directly in Google search results.</p>
<p><strong>3. GetApp</strong>. Gartner-owned comparison shopping platform for SMBs. Free listing. Shares a vendor portal with Capterra and Software Advice. One account unlocks three directories.</p>
<p><strong>4. Software Advice</strong>. Gartner-owned enterprise buyer platform. Free listing. Human advisors guide buyers to the right software. Phone-based consultations drive high-quality leads.</p>
<p><strong>5. TrustRadius</strong>. Unbiased B2B product reviews. No paid placements in rankings. Free listing. Buyers trust TrustRadius because money does not influence product positions.</p>
<p><strong>6. Trustpilot</strong>. Google-visible review platform. Free listing. Reviews appear as rich snippets in search results. Critical for building social proof across every channel.</p>
<p><strong>7. AlternativeTo</strong>. Users search for alternatives to software they already use. Free submission. Highest-intent audience on any directory. People come here ready to switch tools.</p>
<p><strong>8. SaaSHub</strong>. Independent SaaS marketplace with alternative discovery. Free listing. DR 70+. Clean interface. Good for products that compete with well-known tools.</p>
<p><strong>9. SourceForge</strong>. Developer and open-source focused platform. 30M+ monthly visitors. Free listing. Strong <a href="/glossary/domain-authority/">domain authority</a>. One of the oldest software directories online.</p>
<p><strong>10. SoftwareSuggest</strong>. India-focused B2B software discovery. Free listing. If you target the Indian market or want visibility in Asia, this is the primary software directory.</p>
<p><strong>11. Crozdesk</strong>. B2B SaaS comparison and review platform. Free listing. Includes a software comparison engine. Good for enterprise and mid-market products.</p>
